<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="h-auto" lang="fr">
  <head>
    <title>MCBD | Mot de passe oublié ?</title>
  </head>
  <section class="container my-auto py-5">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-sm-12 col-lg-8 col-xl-6 m-auto">
        <div class="card border-0 shadow">
          <div class="card-body header">
            <form class="custom-form" action="/users/password" method="POST">
              <input type="hidden" name="authenticity_token" value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>">
              <div class="margin-top-sign text-center">
                <h2 class="fw-bold text-white">Mot de passe oublié ?</h2>
                <p class="mt-1 mb-4 text-light">Ça arrive à tout le monde, nous allons te renvoyer un email pour réinitialiser ton mot de passe !</p>
              </div>
              <div class="margin-top-form form-floating mb-3 w-75 mx-auto">
                <input id="email" name="user[email]" type="email" autocomplete="email" required class="form-control">
                <label for="email" class="text-dark">Email</label>
              </div>

              <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mt-5">
                <button type="submit" class="site-btn w-50 p-2 mx-auto d-block">Envoyez moi un email</button>
              </div>
              <p class="text-center text-muted mt-5 mb-0">Tu as retrouvé ton mot de passe ? <a href="/users/sign_in" class="fw-bold text-light"><u>Connecte-toi</u></a><br>
              <a href="/users/sign_up" class="fw-bold text-light"><u>Inscris-toi</u></a> si tu n'as pas encore de compte ! </p></p>
            </form>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</html>
